        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Using everyday objects, her bare hands, and her legendary sense of surprise, the seasoned television puppeteer Ingrid Hansen (Fraggle Rock / Jim Henson Co. and Sesame Workshop) creates surreal and hilarious situations with her bare hands, miniature environments, and modeling clay."
